FBIS4-60442 "drnes101_j_94018" FBIS-NES-94-101 Daily Report 24 May 1994 ARABIAN PENINSULA Yemen Radio Reports French Statement of Support for Unity Radio Reports French Statement of Support for Unity JN2405175494 Sanaa Yemeni Republic Radio Network in Arabic 1700 GMT 24 May 94 JN2405175494 Sanaa Yemeni Republic Radio Network Arabic BFN [Text] France, through its foreign minister, has expressed its concern for the preservation of Yemeni unity. Asked by a Cairo radio correspondent about France's stand on the developments in Yemen, French Foreign Minister Alain Juppe said: As a general rule, France believes that the Yemen unity, rather than secession, constitutes a factor of stability. Therefore, we prefer that Yemen unity is respected.
